com.facebook.swift.codec.metadata

Class ThriftType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.swift.codec.metadata.ThriftType

  • @Immutable
public class ThriftType
extends Object
    ThriftType contains all metadata necessary for converting the java type to and from Thrift.
